    "collapsible_content_i7LadG": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_PgPkEF": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you work with clients remotely?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<h5>Absolutely! I can collaborate with you no matter where you are. You can expect a straightforward and transparent design process, with involvement every step of the way—from initial sketches to the final creation. With regular updates, photos, and videos, you’ll be part of the entire process, ensuring your finished piece is exactly as you imagined—no surprises, just the joy of seeing your vision come to life.</h5><h5>Consultations are available via phone, video, or your preferred method. Feel free to <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">email me</span> or <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">schedule a virtual consultation</span> to start your custom jewelry journey.</h5>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_KHntwt": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use my own stones in one of your designs?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<h5>Definitely! Using your heirloom stones in a new piece is a great way to honor your history and update your style. It’s eco-friendly and cost-effective. To get started, send photos and details about your stones so I can design something that perfectly showcases them.</h5><h5>Please note, I’m not liable for any damage to your gemstones during removal from old settings or the setting process in a new piece. They may have pre-existing wear that affects their integrity. If concerned, you can have the piece designed and fabricated by me, then set by your local jeweler.</h5>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_rC9LBw": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long will it take to make my custom jewelry? Do you offer Rush Service?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<h5>The timeframe for crafting handmade jewelry varies based on design complexity. If you have a specific design ready, we can proceed quickly. If you're still deciding, the design stage may take longer. Enjoying the collaborative process without rushing is key.</h5><h5>After finalizing the design, simpler pieces typically take 2-3 weeks, while intricate designs may take up to 6 weeks. Quality craftsmanship takes time but is worth the wait.</h5><h5>If you’re on a tight schedule, please let me know. I’ll do my best to ensure timely delivery and keep you updated with photos and progress reports throughout the process.</h5><h5>For faster options, consider my ready-to-wear collection, which can often be customized quickly.</h5><h5>Please reach out to discuss your timeline needs. Depending on your design, I might be able to expedite the creation.</h5>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_BJBfkh": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I design jewelry for someone without involving them directly?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<h5>To design jewelry discreetly, observe their current style and note the types of jewelry they wear and appreciate. You can also seek insights from their close friends.</h5><h5>If they have distinct tastes, consider involving them to ensure they love the final product and enjoy the process. For surprise moments like engagements, use a placeholder ring.</h5><h5>Focus first on the overall design rather than specifics like gem characteristics. We can refine details like diamond cut or gemstone type later, ensuring a special and collaborative final design.</h5>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_aQFFgD": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I customize a piece I see on your website?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<h5>Absolutely! I can adapt any design to fit your preferences, including changing gems, selecting a different metal, or adding personalized details like engravings. Each modification makes your piece uniquely yours.</h5><h5>If you don't find exactly what you're looking for, I can also craft completely custom pieces inspired by your personal tastes and story. You can be as involved as you like in the design process, ensuring the final piece is a one-of-a-kind heirloom.</h5><h5>Learn more about the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Custom Design Process</span>.</h5>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
