    "slideshow_BBHtJm": {
      "type": "slideshow",
      "blocks": {
        "slide_FCVigj": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Breanne_Logan_Testimonial_Slide.jpg",
            "heading": "–Breanne",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "subheading": "“My husband and I are a quirky couple. For our last anniversary he created a handmade Tardis from <em>Doctor Who</em> — see what I mean? Quirky. After he proposed, I began the search for a wedding band that would reflect who we were as a couple; not only the journey we had taken, but where we hoped our path would lead. Finding Stacey was like finding that perfect wedding gown, the one you <em>know</em> you’re going to walk down the aisle in.”",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_weHmB8": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Brett_and_Cindy_Testimonial_Slide_eb116b6b-5af2-457e-8cd0-5a8a82c8c220.jpg",
            "heading": "–B.",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "subheading": "“After dating only six months, C. and I knew we’d be spending our lives together. However, a formal proposal loomed.. . My grandmother had given me her earring, which led me to the Jewelry Mart to see about repurposing the gems. After they pronounced the rubies cracked and the diamonds too small, and suggested a gaudier token of my affections, I knew I had to find a jewelry designer who could appreciate my grandmother’s contribution.”",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_CHNBpE": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sarah_Zaner_Necklace_Custom_Testimonial.jpg",
            "heading": "–Sarah",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "subheading": "Sarah asked me to make something special with a family heirloom: a gorgeous, big blue topaz. The substantial briolette became the focal point of a romantic Edwardian-influenced necklace. The perfect complement to her wedding gown, it hung precisely in the “V” of her halter-neck: “I described it all to Stacey in words that you would never imagine could successfully translate into a single piece of jewelry and Stacey made it come to life.\"",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_aA4PGi": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Noelle_Jeremy_Testimonial_Slide.jpg",
            "heading": "–Noelle",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "subheading": "“I looked into a custom ring because I wanted more control over the outcome and cost. Stacey and I pored over pictures as I tried to explain my vision; at first, there were so many looks that appealed to me that I had difficulty expressing what I wanted. That initial creative process was most beneficial, because she saw what I liked and created a ring that truly spoke to my style.”",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_4GcANj": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Chris_Lyrica_Testimonial_Slide.jpg",
            "heading": "–Chris",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "subheading": "\"The first person who knew I was going to propose, Stacey was a trusted co-conspirator every step of the way — from suggesting strategies for measuring Lyrica’s ring finger, to providing ideas for engagement rings, and ultimately designing the wedding rings we wear every day.”",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_kwTnqb": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Allison_Eric_Testimonial_Slide.jpg",
            "heading": "–Allison",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "subheading": "“I might have been the least helpful client a jewelry designer could have, but thankfully, Stacey is incredibly patient and encouraging. With her gentle and tenacious guidance, she coaxed out the qualities I valued, and edited out the superfluous.”",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_KBELYi": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Jason_Karli_Commitment_Testimonial.jpg",
            "heading": "–Jason",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "subheading": "“i look at these rings everyday. one iwear everyday of course. they are the most beautiful reminders of not just ourwedding, the fact that we are married, our kids and all that goes with creatinga life together, but also what we want our future together to be, what we wantour lives to be. the rings hold, reflect, and remind us of some of the mostprecious and important ideas of our life together.”",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_N3rTLb": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Mike_Kasey_Commitment_Testimonial.jpg",
            "heading": "–Mike",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "subheading": "\"We wanted a custom ring because to us that feels special and unique. We really liked that you met with us, did a little interview to learn about us and then worked on crafting the ring...that feels more 'right' to me than some mass-produced ring. In the end, I got a beautiful, masculine ring that was made just for me. I won't ever see another like it, and it will stay in my family for ever.<em>\"</em>",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_xTBHQa": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Erik_Elizabeth_Commitment_Testimonial.jpg",
            "heading": "–J.",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "subheading": "\"When Elizabeth approached me to create her rings, she captivated me with her plans to sail the Pacific on an extended honeymoon. It seemed like the perfect way to launch a lifetime of adventure. I get a vicarious thrill every time I see the beautiful photos of her on her voyage across the blue velvet ocean. Have ring — will travel.<em>\"</em>",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "image_overlay_opacity": 0,
            "color_scheme": "background-1",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center"
          }
        },
        "slide_wU6J9M": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Seth_Julianna_Commitment_Testimonial.jpg",
            "heading": "–Julianna",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "subheading": " “Somehow, Stacey divined all of our years into these gorgeous pieces we’re still so moved to have. I’m a drummer and an artist and a gardener. My fingernails are inevitably a disaster and I’ve barely worn jewelry in my life. So it’s all the more wonderful to feel so enchanted by the rings I wear, to feel that even in their imperishable loveliness, they are so perfectly me.”",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "box_align": "middle-center",
            "show_text_box": true,
